FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_3_DETAIL = Late-game traits, heavy pressure, mythic~n~escalation, and more punishing route~n~control. Enemy: Late-game traits, heavy~n~pressure, mythic escalation, and more~n~punishing route control. Loot: Late boss~n~parts, rare caches, and high-end specialist~n~goods dominate value. 보스es: The mastermind~n~network and mythic confrontation path come~n~fully into view. Recipes: 등급 4 boss/relic~n~modifications and war-room-scale support~n~upgrades open. Story: The final act is fully~n~armed and the ranch is directly endangered.~n~Routes: Safe travel is mostly gone; the~n~frontier must be navigated as a campaign~n~map. Checkpoint: Next gate: 레벨 22, 유물 5, 보스~n~처치 3 Unlock Package: Ash Frontier War Pack
FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_3_LABEL = WT 4 | Ash Frontier | 잠김 | Pending | Ash~n~Frontier War Pack
FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_4_DETAIL = Post-ending legendary sandbox with endless~n~elite and hunt pressure. Enemy: Post-ending~n~legendary sandbox with endless elite and~n~hunt pressure. Loot: Endless legendary~n~farming and prestige collection 루트 remain~n~active. 보스es: 보스es return in hunt form and~n~the frontier stays dangerous after the~n~ending. Recipes: Post-ending mastery and~n~repeatable high-risk reward loops stay open.~n~Story: John has ended the war, but not every~n~scar, rumor, or hunt. Routes: Beecher's Hope~n~remains the hub while the whole map stays~n~viable for endless play. Checkpoint: Next~n~gate: 레벨 30, 작업대 등급 4, 월드 티어 4 Unlock~n~Package: After The Ledger Master Pack~n~Package State: Pending
